owever, while the\nsupra-arcade region was a dynamic region consisting of small-scale structures,\nthe CXS seemed to be smooth, structureless. We run simulations using real and\nsynthetic RHESSI data, but we did not find any strong evidence that the CXS had\nany small-scale structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2017 16:47:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-01"}
