 by static FAPs. We perform numerical evaluation to validate our\nanalytical results. We also show that the order-optimal strategy strictly\noutperforms a baseline approach, where the replication sets at mobile devices\nand static FAPs are optimized separately.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Feb 2017 04:44:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Jul 2017 06:52:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 19 Mar 2018 07:08:23 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 29 Oct 2018 15:15:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-30"}
