e that a thorough\ndistinction of El Ni\\~no and La Ni\\~na into their two respective flavors could\nbe crucial for understanding the emergence of strong regional\nhydrometeorological anomalies and anticipating their associated ecological and\nsocioeconomic impacts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Feb 2017 12:12:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Oct 2020 10:55:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2020 15:30:04 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 8 Jan 2021 10:40:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-11"}
